{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act33side_level_act33side_09_end","storyGroup":"act33side","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"act33side_level_act33side_09_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BB-9","storyName":"尘埃落定","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"重伤的特蕾西娅凭着最后的力气将“文明的存续”交给了阿米娅，而在此时出现在特蕾西娅面前的人是博士。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act33side/level_act33side_09_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act33side_09","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":18,"next":20,"characters":["特蕾西娅","阿米娅","博士"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"charslot","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_monastery_nomal.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_bg_bg_light.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":7},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅最后记得的事，是她睡在黑色的泡泡里。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅温柔地抱着包裹着她的泡泡。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"讲述着一个她已经听过许多次的故事......","id":12},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"在绝望的沙漠里有很多恐怖的影子，他们追逐着不停寻找希望的小布人。","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"黑袍的影子是最古老最古老的，绝望和悲哀的回声。","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"一旦被他们抓住，就再也逃不开了。","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"在沙漠中，小布人遇到了缀满赤金与宝石的国王，他答应小布人只要原路返回，就给他数不尽的财富。","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"尽管国王拉扯着他，小布人依旧丢下了诱人的宝石继续前进。","id":20},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但很快——","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"黑袍的影子追上了他。影子不断向他扑去，无穷无尽......","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"“砰，砰，砰”......","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他只能抽出针和线做的长矛与黑色的影子战斗，最终挡开了影子们的利爪继续向前逃去......","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"直到逃到一条泪水汇成的大河。没有船只，没有浮萍，小布人只能游过去......","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"可一沾上泪水，他就越来越沉，直至河底——","id":28},{"type":"dialog","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":30},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他失败了。","id":32},{"type":"charslot","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"这就是故事的结局了吗？阿米娅不愿意相信。","id":34},{"type":"text","text":"也许是特蕾西娅小姐念错了也说不定？","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"她焦急地想要让特蕾西娅小姐改变结局......","id":36},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","focus":"n","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"特蕾西娅小姐......","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......我在。","id":40},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们......能救救小布人吗？","id":42},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你想要救他吗？","id":44},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"想，我......很想很想......","id":46},{"type":"dialog","id":47},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"3","id":48},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_underwtr","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"un","id":49},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"un","fadetime":"3","id":50},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":52},{"type":"charslot","id":53},{"type":"background","id":54},{"type":"text","text":"声音淡去了。","id":55},{"type":"text","text":"挡住阿米娅视线的泡泡在消散。","id":56},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅的身影在她的眼前越来越清晰——","id":57},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_dim_openeye","layer":"1","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":60},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":62},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"un","fadetime":"4","id":63},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":64},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.2","r":"0.92","g":"0.4","b":"0.3","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"在眼角的余光中，她看到了躺倒在地面上的黑袍影子们渗出的殷红。","id":66},{"type":"text","text":"这些人......是谁？他们是什么时候来的？为什么会躺在地上？","id":67},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅有太多太多的疑惑想要问特蕾西娅，她努力睁大自己的眼睛......","id":68},{"type":"text","text":"她看到了白色衣服上沾染的殷红。看到了......特蕾西娅泛红的眼角。","id":69},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅小姐还好吗？","id":70},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅想问问特蕾西娅小姐身上的伤势。","id":71},{"type":"text","text":"但她发不出声音。","id":72},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.4","id":74},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......阿米娅，没事。","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我在这呢。那些故事里的坏蛋已经暂时被打倒了。","id":77},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":79},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅小姐怎么了？","id":80},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅想要拭去特蕾西娅小姐脸上的疲惫。","id":81},{"type":"text","text":"但她抬不起自己的手。","id":82},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":84},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"charslot","id":86},{"type":"background","id":87},{"type":"image","image":"49_i17","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":88},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.15","yScaleTo":"1.15","duration":"40","block":"false","id":89},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":90},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"抱歉，我没有能力改变故事的结局。","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但是你可以，阿米娅......","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你会走上一条艰难的道路。就像试图跨越泪水之河的小布人。","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我能够帮上你的，唯有将这顶黑色的冠冕赠与你。","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"万年的时间，我的族群因为历史的局限性，错误地使用了这顶冠冕。","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"它被污染，被绑定。但本不该如此。","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"如果要打破诅咒，打破命运......我需要你的帮助。","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你愿意改写结局吗？","id":99},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅想要说出“愿意”，但她无法发出声音。","id":100},{"type":"text","text":"她焦急地点着头，她想，也许至少这样能够帮上特蕾西娅小姐......","id":101},{"type":"text","text":"能够救她——","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"虽然我现在剩下的力量能做的不多，但足以将它的权限转移给你。","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我为你封存了它的大部分区域，以免无边无际的信息搅乱你的思绪。","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅......抱歉，我将这顶冠冕的重量压在了你的身上。","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我本以为......我能够陪伴你的日子还有好久好久，陪伴你长大，陪伴你到能勇敢地面对父母的离去，陪伴你到能自己给出回答——","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"回答你是否愿意替我继续走下去......","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但留给我们的时间总是不够，阿米娅。","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我如今自私地将我所背负的重担压在了你的身上......","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"对不起，孩子——","id":111},{"type":"dialog","id":112},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_daggerslow","volume":"1","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"image","image":"49_i19","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","fadetime":"0","id":115},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":117},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅试图喊出声，但她却无法张开口，甚至无法挪动自己的四肢。","id":119},{"type":"text","text":"黑色的剑刃似乎穿透了自己的胸口。","id":120},{"type":"text","text":"她理应感受到痛苦。但那柄剑留下的——","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"唯有温热。充满期盼的温热。","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"阿米娅，它是希望，亦是痛苦。","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你会困惑，会犹疑。","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"但请相信，凯尔希医生会永远站在你的身边。","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"她会帮助你去探究，去重新接近存续的秘密。","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你能克服的，对吧，阿米娅......","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你一直都是一个坚强到令我都惊讶的孩子。","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"呼......","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我真的很累了。","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"谢谢你，阿米娅，这些日子，是你将快乐带给了我。","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"现在，先暂且休息片刻吧。睡吧......","id":132},{"type":"text","text":"安心地睡吧。","id":133},{"type":"text","text":"我会一直陪着你。","id":134},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":136},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"charslot","id":138},{"type":"image","id":139},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":141},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":142},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":144},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅听到了熟悉的声音。","id":145},{"type":"dialog","id":146},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":147},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......阿米娅！","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":150},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅并未抬头看向到来的人。","id":151},{"type":"text","text":"王冠抽离，又重聚。而她的气息却愈发微弱。","id":152},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......博士。你何必来到这里呢。","id":154},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我感到了......你的情感。我看见了，你的过去。","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"可你本可以待在别处，静待我的死亡到来。你知道这一次，我不会逃离，也不会撤退。","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你来，是为了找阿米娅吗？还是为了......","id":160},{"type":"dialog","id":161},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"1","id":162},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":163},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":164},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅已经不用听那个人的回答。","id":165},{"type":"text","text":"在那人的身后，潮水般的刺客不断从阴影中涌来，奔向了特蕾西娅——","id":166},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这就是你的答案吧，博士......","id":168},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":172},{"type":"charslot","id":173},{"type":"background","id":174},{"type":"image","id":175}],"characters":["特蕾西娅","阿米娅","博士"]}